00:09:25.090 --> 00:09:27.710
You have the same type of
metadata, access to the same

00:09:27.710 --> 00:09:31.830
thumbnails, downloading files
is pretty much the same,

00:09:31.830 --> 00:09:34.010
regardless of which API
you use to actually

00:09:34.010 --> 00:09:35.390
search for the content.

00:09:35.390 --> 00:09:37.570
So it shouldn't be that
difficult of a

00:09:37.570 --> 00:09:39.570
